<HEADLINE>
FT  29 JUL 93 / World News in Brief: Boy accused of murder
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A boy of 16 was accused of the murder of Akhlaq Ahmed Razzaq, aged 9, whose
body was found in a park near his home in Slough, Berks.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
